# Model D 3-oscillator demo — a fat bass riff + a held chord, default patch.
# frames 600  fps 60  scale 2
bpm 120
start 2
# a chord stab (A=C, D=E, G=G held together) — hear the 3 osc + detune beat
beat 0  tap A 4
beat 0  tap D 4
beat 0  tap G 4
# walking bass line, each note a quick hold
beat 4  tap A 1
beat 5  tap F 1
beat 6  tap D 1
beat 7  tap S 1
beat 8  tap A 2
beat 10 tap G 2
# big sustained chord to close
beat 12 tap A 6
beat 12 tap F 6
beat 12 tap K 6
